# Financial Risk Credit Off Balance Sheet Non Market Related Other Transactions ARF 112 2A Amount

## identifier
de7934

## type
float

## definition
This is a balancing item in the list in which it is being used.

This is the value, as at the relevant date, of all other non-market-related off-balance sheet transactions giving rise to credit risk, as to be reported on form ARF_112_2A.

This item represents total non-market related off-balance sheet transactions giving rise to credit risk, other than those transactions classified as any of the following:
- Direct credit substitutes;
- Performance-related contingencies;
- Trade-related contingencies;
- Lending of securities or posting of securities as collateral;
- Assets sold with recourse;
- Forward asset purchases;
- Partly paid shares and securities;
- Placements of forward deposits;
- Note issuance and underwriting facilities;
- Credit derivatives used for acquiring credit risk exposure; or
- Other commitments.

## syntax
### xbrl
- balance=debit
- name=FinancialRisk.Credit.OffBalanceSheetNonMarketRelatedOtherTransactionsARF1122A.Amount
- classification=baf/bafot/bafot.02.06
- period=instant
